## Critical Success Factors (User Perspective)
- Clear, minimal steps; no confusion about what to do next.
- Correct RTL/LTR and language-specific copy (Arabic vs English).
- Downloaded image looks correct: readable text, proper layout, brand-consistent (Satorp, #2F388D).
- Works on typical mobile and desktop browsers (no special plugins).

## Product Vision Summary
A single-page (or minimal multi-step) flow where the employee chooses language, picks one of three greeting messages, adds their name, and downloads a finished card image—all with consistent branding and no account required.
